				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$ \kappa_{2} = (n - 1)(n - 2)^{2} / (^{ 2} P_{i} )^{ 2} . $$\end{document}

